From 9f7d03f0c8395bcf951477f036c5bfa8574a0f08 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?=C3=98yvind=20Harboe?= <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
Date: Sun, 29 Mar 2026 23:14:03 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 02/31] build: add exports_files BUILD.bazel to all src/
 directories
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Every flow/designs/src/<name>/ directory now has a BUILD.bazel with
exports_files and a :verilog filegroup, enabling both single-file
and glob references from orfs_flow() targets.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Signed-off-by: Øyvind Harboe <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
